Wani Karamin Alade Ya Kashe Wani Manomi a China
Rahotanni sun ce wani manomi ya fuskanci hari kuma wani alade ya kashe shi a kasuwa a kudu maso yammacin China.
Jaridar Morning Post ta ruwaito a ranar Lahadi cewa an gano mutumin, wanda aka bayyana shi da Yuan,  ya mutu kuma an fasa jijiyar zuciyarsa, a cikin kwarin jini kusa da kasuwar aladu a Liupanshui, lardin Guihou, Kudancin China.
Wani manomi yana shirin ya yi wa aladu allurar rigakafi a cikin gida, a ranar 30 ga Mayu, 2005, a lardin Qinghai, da ke ƙasar Sin.
An ba da rahoton cewa ya tafi tare da ɗan'uwansa daga lardin Yunnan da ke kusa a ranar Laraba don su sayar da aladu 15 a kasuwa.
Washegari, ɗan'uwansa ya same shi ya mutu, kuma ya ga ƙofar gidan aladun a buɗe.
Ya ce a cikin ƙugiya akwai babban alade da jini ya cika bakinsa.
Rahoton ya ce, likitocin sun tabbatar da cewa naman alade mai nauyin kilo 249 da rabi ne ya kashe manoman.
An ambata ɗan kawunsa mai suna Wu a cikin Guiyang Evening New cewa: Ƙafafun ɗan kawuna suna cike da jini kuma suna taƙama.
Kamara ta tsaro ta kama Yuan yana shiga kasuwa da karfe 4:40 na safe ranar Alhamis don ciyar da aladunsa.
An gano gawarsa bayan awa ɗaya.
Wannan dabbar da ta kashe mutum ba ta Yuan ba ce ko kuma ɗan'uwansa.
Manajan kasuwar ya gaya wa jaridar Evening News cewa an tsare aladun don kada ya sake kai hari, yayin da 'yan sanda suke tattara shaidu a wurin.
An ce iyalin Yuan da kuma masu kula da kasuwar suna tattaunawa don su yi ta'aziyya domin mutuwarsa.
Ko da yake ba a yawan yin hakan ba, an taɓa yin rahoton cewa aladu sun kai wa mutane hari a dā.
A shekara ta 2016, wani alade ya kai wa matarsa da mijinta hari a gonarsu a jihar Massachusetts, kuma ya bar mutumin da raunuka masu tsanani.
Shekaru goma da suka shige, wani alade mai nauyin kilo 295 ya yi wa wani manomi ɗan ƙasar Wales barazana a kan tarakta har sai da matarsa ta tsoratar da shi.
Bayan da aladun wani manomi suka ci naman aladunsa a Oregon a shekara ta 2012, wani manomi a Manitoba ya gaya wa CBC News cewa aladun ba sa yawan kasancewa a cikin daji amma idan suka ɗanɗana jinin zai iya sa su fara cin naman.
Ya ce: Suna son yin wasa.
Suna kama da yara, suna son sanin abin da ke faruwa ... ba sa son su yi maka lahani.
