Shugaba Donald Trump ya kaddamar da yakin neman zabensa a wannan daren a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tafiye-tafiye biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, har da zuwa wurare masu kyau kamar su Tennessee da Mississippi.
Game da kuri'ar tabbatar da shugabancin, da aka dakatar da shi na ɗan lokaci don cike gurbin da ke cikin Kotun Koli, Trump ya yi niyyar samar da goyon baya ga zaɓen da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar rashin rinjaye a majalisa a zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne ake kallon fim ɗin Trump a yammacin Virginia?
Za a fara bikin Wheeling na Trump a yammacin Virginia da ƙarfe 7 na yamma, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018
Za ku iya kallon bikin na Trump a West Virginia a kan layi ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Trump zai iya yin jawabi a Kotun Koli a wannan makon a lokacin da ake sauraron shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya yi tashin hankali yayin da ake gabatar da tuhumar fyade saboda dakatar da kuri'ar tabbatar da amincewa da FBI ta yi na makonni biyu.
Amma manufar wannan jerin abubuwan da aka yi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar ƙalubale a zaɓen Nuwamba su inganta matsayinsu.
Wannan shi ne dalilin da ya sa yakin neman zaben da aka yi a makon gobe, ya nuna cewa masu zane-zane biyar na shirin su na neman masu sa kai da masu goyon baya a lokacin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin kare da kuma fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai, in ji Reuters.
Ikon majalisa yana da muhimmanci ga manufarsa har shugaban ya kai ziyara wurare da dama a lokacin zagaye na zabe, in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa a Reuters
An shirya bikin da yamma a filin wasa na Wesbanco a birnin Wheeling, kuma za a yi amfani da shi a kan wasu 'yan kallo daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma za a gabatar da shi a kan wani dandalin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai kai ziyara karo na biyu a West Virginia, inda ya samu kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da ya kada a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia Patrick Morrisey, wanda ya fadi a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa zai yi kokarin taimaka masa a zaben ba", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
