China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar sababbin mutane da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV/AIDS da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin tana samun karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na masu kamuwa da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a ƙasar, in ji masu kula da lafiyar.
An samu aƙalla shari'o'i 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekara ta 2018 kaɗai.
Yawancin sababbin shari'o'in na ƙwayoyin cuta ne, kuma hakan ya kawo canji a yanayin idan aka kwatanta da na dā.
A al'ada, cutar HIV tana yaɗuwa da sauri a wasu wurare a ƙasar Sin ta wurin jinin da ke da cutar.
Amma adadin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar a wannan hanyar ya ragu kuma ya kusan kai kashi ɗaya, in ji ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Ko da yake, kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a ƙasar Sin yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i abu ne mai tsanani ga mutanen da suke son jima'i da kuma luwadi.
An halatta jima'i tsakanin mutane na jinsi ɗaya a ƙasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma ana nuna wa mutanen da suke da jinsi ɗaya wariya
Domin al'adu da suke hana mutum yin jima'i, bincike ya kimanta cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da suke jima'i da maza suna aurar mata.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne domin rashin kāriya na namiji a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin ƙasar Sin ta yi alkawarin ba da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin sashe na magance matsalar.
