Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da 'tsoratar da' 'yan kasuwa na karya'
Bayan mako guda da wata jarida mai suna China ta wallafa wani talla na shafuffuka huɗu game da Amirka da ke sūkar cinikin Amurka da China, jakadan Amirka ya zargi Gwamnatin China da yin amfani da jaridar Amirka don yaɗa ƙarya.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba da ta gabata ya yi magana a kan jaridar China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da aka fi sayarwa a jihar - bayan ya zargi China da son tsoma baki a zaben majalisa na Amurka a ranar 6 ga watan Oktoba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Trump ya yi wa gwamnatin China zagon kasa saboda tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, abin da jami'an gwamnatin Amurka suka fada wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters, ya nuna cewa wannan sabon mataki ne na gaggawar yakin neman zaben da gwamnatin Amurka ke yi a kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake yana da kyau gwamnatocin ƙasashe su yi talla don su ƙarfafa kasuwanci, China da Amirka suna gasa sosai a harkokin kasuwanci, suna ɗaga haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa daga ƙasashen waje.
An yi amfani da harajin da China ta yi don a hukunta ƙasashe kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana a harkokin Sin da Amirka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Gwamnatin China ta yi wa ma'aikata, manoma da kuma 'yan kasuwa na Amurka lahani.
Branstad ya rubuta a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi cewa, "yanzu China tana yin amfani da injinmu na buga littattafai da ba ta biya kuɗin shiga ba, ta wajen yin tallace-tallace na ƙarya".
"Don yaɗa wannan ƙarya", in ji Branstad, "gwamnatin China ta ɗauki al'adar Amirka na 'yancin magana da kuma buga littattafai kyauta ta wajen saka talla da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register".
Ya ce: "A wani ɓangare kuma, idan ka bi wannan titi na Beijing, za ka ga mutane kaɗan ne kawai da suke nuna rashin gamsuwa, kuma ba za ka ga yadda mutanen China suke ji game da matsalar tattalin arziki da ke ci gaba a ƙasar ba, domin Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta ƙasar Sin tana sarrafa kafofin watsa labarai sosai".
Ya daɗa cewa wata jarida mai suna China ta yi jinkirin buga talifinsa, ko da yake ba ta faɗi jaridar ba.
