Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican suka haɗa kai don su kāre ɗan takarar Majalisar Dokoki Brett Kavanaugh da ake tuhuma da cin zarafin mata, masu bincike sun yi gargaɗi cewa mata da yawa za su ji haka, musamman a lokacin zaɓen da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara.
Wannan batu ne mai ban tsoro, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican ba su so su yi zabe ba.
Waɗannan ba su da sauƙi", in ji Grant Reeher, masanin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a cikin wata jarida mai suna The Hill da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce bai yi imani cewa ƙoƙarin da aka yi na yi wa Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) na FBI bincike ba zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa ƙuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko kuma a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun ƙungiyar MoveOn, a ranar Jumma'a, in ji jaridar Washington, D.C.
A ranar Jumma'a da safe, masu fafutuka sun yi ihu suna cewa "Pudungunu yana zuwa!" yayin da suke zanga-zanga a cikin farfajiyar majalisar dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zaɓi su ci gaba da naɗa Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dokta Christine Blasey Ford, in ji rahoton Mic.
"Himma da kuma motsawar dimokiradiyya za su zama abin da ya fi kyau", in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai sharhi game da siyasa, a cikin labarai.
"Mutane suna cewa wannan batu ne mai muhimmanci; gaskiya ne.
Zai fi muhimmanci, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa ƙuri'a da ke zaune a birane da kuma matasa masu jefa ƙuri'a, masu shekara 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, ba sa yawan jefa ƙuri'a".
Ko da kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a fili game da zargin da ake yi wa wanda aka naɗa a Kotun Koli na yin lalata, wani mai sharhi ya ce zai zama abin ƙyama idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da yin hakan.
"Wannan ya zama abin ƙyama ga jam'iyyar GOP", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na Ƙasa, a farkon makon da ya gabata, in ji NBC News.
"Ba batun zaɓen kwamitin ba ne ko kuma zaɓen ƙarshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai shiga cikin jerin alƙalai, batun yadda 'yan Republican suke bi da matar ne", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, wani rukunin da ke taimaka wa 'yan Democrat su yi zabe, a cikin labarai.
Amma, kamar dai Amirkawa sun rarrabu a kan wanda za su gaskata da shi sa'ad da shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh suka bayyana, kuma da yawa suna goyon bayan Kavanaugh.
Wani sabon bincike da aka yi a kan YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin ɗari na waɗanda suka amsa sun gaskata da shaidar Ford, kuma kashi 35 cikin ɗari sun gaskata da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin wataƙila ko kuma Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya a shaidarsa, amma kashi 30 ne kawai suka gaskata da abin da Ford ya ce.
Bayan shawarar da Flake ya bayar, FBI yanzu tana bincika tuhumar da Ford ya kawo da kuma mai tuhumar, Deborah Ramirez, in ji rahoton jaridar The Guardian.
Ford ya shaida wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa Kavanaugh da ya sha giya ya yi masa lalata sa'ad da yake ɗan shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi gunaguni cewa wani ɗan Majalisar Maɗaukaki ya nuna masa al'aurarsa a lokacin da suke liyafa a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
