Bernard Vann: An ba da lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
An girmama firist na Cocin Czech da ya ci lambar Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya a matsayin soja a wani biki da aka yi a garinsu shekaru 100 bayan haka.
Lt. Colonel Reverend Bernard Vann ya ci nasara a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a yaƙin da aka yi a Bellenglise da kuma Lehaucourt.
Amma bayan kwana huɗu, wani ya kashe shi a ɓoye, ba tare da ya san cewa ya ci lambar yabo mafi girma da ake bayarwa a ƙasar Britaniya ba.
'Yan'uwansa maza biyu sun buɗe wani abin tunawa a ranar Asabar a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Wani jikansa mai suna Michael Vann ya ce wannan "abin tunawa ne" da aka yi na cika shekara 100 da samun kyautar gwarzo da kakansa ya yi.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a cewar jaridar London Gazette, Lieutenant Vann ya ja-goranci sojoji dubu ɗaya ko kuma rukunin sojoji su ƙetare Canal de Saint-Quentin "duk da ƙanƙara da hayaki mai ƙarfi da ke fitowa daga fagen yaƙi da kuma bindigogi".
Daga baya ya yi hanzari zuwa wajen yaƙi kuma "da gaba gaɗi mai girma" ya ja su zuwa gaban rundunar yaƙi da yaƙi ɗaya kuma ya kashe uku cikin sojojin abokan gaba.
Wani ɗan Jamus ya harbi Lieutenant Vann a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wato fiye da wata ɗaya kafin yaƙin ya ƙare.
Michael Vann, ɗan shekara 72, ya ce abin da surukinsa ya yi "wani abu ne da ba zan taɓa mantawa ba amma yana sa ni baƙin ciki".
Ita da ɗan'uwanta Dr. James Vann sun saka furanni a bayan wannan tafiyar, wadda ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ta yi.
Michael Vann ya ce "yana jin kunya sosai da ya sa hannu a wannan tafiyar" kuma ya daɗa cewa "za a iya ganin ƙarfin jarumi ta wurin goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su ba da".
Masu sha'awar MMA sun zauna duk dare suna kallon Bellator 206, amma a maimakon haka an nuna musu Peppa Pig
Ka yi tunanin kana kallon Bellator 206 da dare kuma ka rasa damar ganin babban abin da ya faru.
A cikin jerin daga San Jose, an yi yaƙe-yaƙe 13, an nuna su shida a kan babban katin kuma an watsa su kai tsaye a duk dare a Birtaniya a Channel 5.
Da karfe shida na safe, yayin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald suke shirin yin shayarwa, masu watsa labarai na Burtaniya sun bar mutumin da ke da ƙugiya yayin da aka sauya watsa shirye-shiryen kuma Peppa Pig ta shiga.
Wasu sun yi fushi cewa sun yi barci har asuba don su kalli wasan.
Wani mai amfani da Twitter ya kwatanta yin amfani da 'yan tsana a matsayin "wasa da ba ta dace ba".
"Dole ne a yi amfani da tsarin gwamnati a karfe shida na safe don kada a yi amfani da shirin, saboda haka, ya kamata a yi amfani da shirin yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban kamfanin sayar da kayayyaki da sadarwa na Bellator, sa'ad da aka tambaye shi dalilin canja tsarin.
"Ka ba shi alade, " in ji shi.
Shugaban kamfanin Bellator Scott Coker ya ce za su yi shirin su ma su haɗa da masu yin fim a Burtaniya a nan gaba.
"Ina ganin idan na yi tunanin sake yin wasan, ina ganin wataƙila za a iya yin wani abu", in ji Coker.
"Amma da ƙarfe shida na safe ne a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za mu iya yin kome ba sai ranar Lahadi, ranar Litinin a gare su.
Amma har ila muna yin bincike a kan batun.
Hakika, an aika saƙonni da yawa sa'ad da aka kashe wutar kuma dukansu suna da ban tsoro.
Muna ƙoƙarin gyara raunukan, muna tunanin cewa matsalar fasaha ce.
Amma ba haka ba ne, batun gwamnati ne.
Ina so in tabbatar maka cewa wannan ba zai sake faruwa ba.
Za mu shirya yaƙe-yaƙe biyar maimakon shida - kamar yadda muka saba - muna ƙoƙari mu yi wa masu sha'awarmu wasa amma mun yi ƙari.
Muna baƙin ciki sosai da abin da ya faru".
Discs na Tsibirin Desert: Tom Daley yana da fahariya domin jinsi
Tom Daley, ɗan wasan tsere na Olympics, ya sha wahala sosai a gaban mutane domin jinsi na - amma hakan ya motsa shi ya yi nasara.
Wannan saurayi mai zunubin shekaru 24 ya ce bai fahimci ba har zuwa lokacin da ya shiga makarantar sakandare cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni".
A lokacin da take magana a kan rediyo na 4 Desert Island Discs a matsayin mai gabatar da jawabi mai suna Lauren Laverne, ta yi magana game da 'yancin 'yan luwadi su ba da "bege" ga wasu.
Ta kuma ce, kasancewa iyaye ya sa ba ma damuwa sosai game da samun lambar yabo a gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, wadda take gudanar da wannan taron na tsawon lokaci, ta yi watanni ba ta iya zuwa aiki ba domin rashin lafiya.
Da yake fitowa a matsayin wanda aka yi wa yan wasa a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "ƙasa da kowa idan ya yi nasara domin "ba a yarda da mutane su yi sha'awar samari da 'yan mata ba".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, wannan ra'ayin na kasawa da kuma bambancin da nake da shi, ya ba ni ƙarfi da kuma ƙuduri na yi nasara".
Suna son su tabbatar da cewa shi "wani abu ne", don kada kowa ya yanke shawara sa'ad da suka gano cewa yana da sha'awar jima'i.
Tauraruwar tagulla ta Olympics sau biyu ita ce fitacciyar mai fafutukar kare hakkin LGBT kuma ta yi amfani da halarta a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan bazarar a Ostiraliya don yin kira ga kasashe da yawa da kada su nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi hakan ne domin yana ganin cewa yana da albarka da ya yi rayuwa a fili ba tare da sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu "bege".
Wani ɗan wasan fim mai suna Dustin Lance Black da ya yi aure a shekara ta 2013 ya ce: "Na yi baƙin ciki sosai sa'ad da na soma soyayya da wani mutum".
Daley ta auri wanda ya ci kyautar Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20 a shekarar da ta shige, amma ta ce shekaru ba su da matsala.
"Idan ka sha wahala sosai tun kana yaro" - ta halarci gasar Olympics ta farko sa'ad da take 'yar shekara 14, kuma mahaifinta ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ta ce yana da wuya a sami wanda ya sha wahala kamar ita.
A watan Yuni, ma'auratan suka haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce hakan ya canja "hanayensa".
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, zan ce 'Ina son in ci lambar zinariya,'" in ji shi.
"A gaskiya, akwai abubuwa da suka fi lambar zinariya ta gasar Olympics tamani.
Robbie ne lambar zinariya ta gasar Olympics".
An ba ɗanta sunan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya rasu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 bayan da aka gano cewa yana da ciwon daji a ƙwaƙwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba, kuma ya ce ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da ya roƙa shi ne tikitin jirgin sama na London na 2012 - domin yana son ya yi layi kafin ya mutu.
"Ba zan iya cewa ba, Baba, ba za ka iya zuwa layin gaba ba", in ji ta.
"Sa'ad da ya daina numfashi, ina riƙe da hannunsa, amma bayan ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu ne na fahimci cewa ba abin da ya same shi", in ji ta.
A shekara ta 2012, Daley ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics kuma ya ci tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da nake so a rayuwata - in yi tsalle a gaban 'yan'uwana a gasar Olympics, na ji daɗin hakan sosai", in ji ta.
Wannan ya motsa waƙar da ta zaɓa - Proud for Heather Small - wadda ta motsa ta yayin da take shirin yin gasar Olympics kuma ta sa ta kasance da ƙwazo.
An gabatar da shirin Desert Island Discs a tashar rediyo ta BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da ƙarfe 11:15 na BST.
Mickelson ɗan wasan golf da ya yi rashin lafiya yana zaune a kan benci a Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai kafa sabon tarihi a ranar Lahadi a gasar Ryder Cup ta 47 da ya yi, amma dole ne ya nuna cewa yana da kuzari don kada wannan ƙwarewar ta zama mummunan abu.
Mickelson, wanda ya buga wasan na biyu a shekara ta da ya kafa tarihi na 12, kyaftin Jim Furyk ne ya sa shi a benci a wasan golf na hudu da hudu a ranar Asabar.
Maimakon ya ci nasara, kamar yadda yake a Amirka, wanda ya ci nasara sau biyar a gasar ya yi rabin rana yana ci gaba da yin nasara kuma ya ci gaba da wasa da begen samun kuɗi.
Wannan mutum mai shekara 48 bai taɓa buga ƙwallon ba kuma ko da yake yana motsawa, ba shi da ƙarfi sosai don wasan Le Golf National da ake yi da ƙwalƙwal, inda ƙwallo mai tsawo sau da yawa yakan ci ƙwallo mai gudu.
Kuma idan wasan da kansa bai isa ba, a wasan Mickelson na tara a ranar Lahadi, ya fuskanci mai gabatar da kara na British Open, Francesco Molinari, wanda ya yi wasa da sabon Tommy Fleetwood a babban wasan, don ya ci dukan wasanninsu na wannan makon.
Idan 'yan Amirkawan da suka ci kwallaye huɗu suka fara wasanni 12 da ƙwallon wuta, wasan Mickelson zai zama na musamman.
Furyk ya nuna cewa ya amince da mutumin, ba wai ya yi banza ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci aikin da yake yi a yau sosai, sai ya rungume ni ya sumbace ni kuma ya gaya mini cewa zai kasance a shirye gobe".
"Kyakkyawan mutum ne.
Shi ne Mafi Girma a wasan kuma ya yi wasa mai girma a cikin waɗannan wasannin a baya, da kuma wannan makon.
Ban taɓa ganin shi yana wasa ba.
Na yi tsammanin abubuwa da yawa, amma hakan ya faru kuma mun yi tunanin cewa hakan ya kamata.
Yana son ya nuna kansa, kamar sauran mutane".
Mickelson zai wuce Nick Faldo a gasar Ryder Cup da aka yi a ranar Lahadi.
Wannan zai zama wasansa na ƙarshe a gasar Ryder, wanda ba ya daidaita da tarihin da ya kafa.
