Furyk ya ga bangarorin biyu a babban gasar ƙarshe, inda ya kasance cikin tawagar da ta ci Brookline kafin a ci shi a lokacin da Turai ta gabatar da "Mu'ujiza ta Madinah".
"Na tuna da dukan abin da ya faɗa", in ji shi sa'ad da aka tambaye shi yadda kyaftin din jirgin, Ben Crenshaw, ya ƙarfafa 'yan wasan a ranar ƙarshe a shekara ta 1999.
"Muna da wasanni 12 na wasa gobe, amma kada ku fara da wasa mai ƙarfi kamar yadda kuka gani a Brooklyn, da kuma a Medinah.
