Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesiya
Hukumomi sun ce a kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a lokacin girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da kuma tsunami da ya afkawa birnin Palu da ke ƙasar Indonesia a ranar Jumma'a, kuma ana sa ran cewa adadin zai ƙaru.
Tun da babu hanyar sadarwa, ma'aikatan agaji ba su iya sanin yanayin ba a Donggala, wanda ke arewacin Palu kuma kusa da inda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta fara.
An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palu bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke bakin tekun yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, kuma yana da mazaunan kusan 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana murnar cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa.
Wannan dutse yana da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, wannan yanki da ke ƙarƙashin lardin yana da mazaunan kusan 299,200.
Kamun kifi da noma ne suke sa tattalin arziki a lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin bakin teku na Donngala.
Ma'adinan nickel wani aiki ne mai muhimmanci a wannan lardin, amma ya fi yawa a Morowali, a gefen gaɓar teku na Sulawesi.
Ƙungiyar Taimako ta Indonesiya ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami sun addabi Palu da Donngala sau da yawa.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya sake afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da girgizar ƙasa take yawan faruwa, kuma ana yawan samun girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a yankin a shekarun baya bayan nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gaɓar yamma na lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a yankin Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin mutanen da ke Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa da yawa ta auku a gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Mutane da yawa suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu maso gabashin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta jawo tsunami da ya halaka mutane 700 a gaɓar tekun kudu.
2009: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.6 ta afka kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, kuma ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, wanda ya halaka birane da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh ta yi wa mutane barazana da kuma tsoro yayin da suke tuna asarar da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka yi a shekara ta 2004.
Ba a yi tsunami a wannan lokacin ba, amma gine-gine da suka rushe sun kashe mutane fiye da 100.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa ta yi wa tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonisiya barazana, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, musamman a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gidaje kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido cikin yanayi mai wuya na ɗan lokaci.
