Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun gabatar da takardar neman hukuncin kisa a kan wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin NYC
Masu shari'a a New York suna son a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a New York, wanda ya kashe mutane takwas, hukuncin kisa  wanda ba a taɓa yanke masa ba tun 1953.
An ba da rahoton cewa Saipov, ɗan shekara 30, ya yi hayar wani babban motar haya don ya kai hari a kan masu keke a kan hanyar West Side Highway, Lower Manhattan, yana yi wa masu keke da masu tafiya a ƙafa hari a watan Oktoba.
Don yanke hukuncin kisa, lauyoyi za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya yi wa mutane rauni da gangan, a cewar sanarwar da aka bayar a lokacin da ake neman hukuncin kisa a Jihar Kudancin New York.
Za a iya yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu, in ji takardar kotun.
Makonni bayan harin, kotun ta gabatar da ƙara 22 a kan Saipov, har da takwas na kisan kai da ya shafi cin hanci da rashawa, da kuma shari'ar da lauyoyi suke yi a kan aikata laifi da aka tsara, da kuma na yin faɗa da lalata motoci.
Da suke kwatanta yadda Saipov ya aikata wannan mugun abu, masu laifi, da kuma na ban tsoro, lauyoyi sun ce harin ya bukaci ya zauna ya yi tunani sosai.
Sanarwar ta ce: "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi baƙin ciki sosai, ya sa iyalinsa da abokansa baƙin ciki, har ma ya sa Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da kuma Alejandro Damian Pagnucco suka mutu".
Biyar cikin waɗanda suka mutu yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekara goma kafin wannan lokacin, an yi shari'a mai tsanani a Jihar Kudu ta New York.
An same wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe masu sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu, amma a ƙarshe a watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009, an yanke masa hukuncin ɗaurin rai da rai.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yanke wa Julius da Ethel Rosenberg hukuncin kisa a New York, ma'aurata ne da aka kashe bayan an same su da laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Yaƙin Barazana shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe iyalin Rosenberg a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Masu shari'a sun ce Saipov, ɗan Uzbekistan, bai nuna damuwa ba kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
Wani ɗan sanda ya ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana farin ciki.
Saipov ya gaya wa hukumomi cewa ya motsa shi ya yi hakan bayan ya kalli bidiyon 'yan kungiyar ISIS a wayarsa, bisa ga takardun tuhumar.
'Yar sandan ta ce, ta kuma ce a saka tutar ISIS a ɗakin asibitin da take.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhume-tuhume 22 da aka yi masa.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin lauyoyin da suka wakilci Saipov, ya ce ya yi baƙin ciki sosai da shawarar da mai gabatar da ƙara ya yanke.
Patton ya ce: "Ina ganin cewa shawarar da aka yanke na neman a yanke masa hukuncin kisa maimakon a amince da wanda ake tuhuma ya yi ikirarin laifinsa kuma a yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da an sake shi ba, zai ƙara tsawon lokacin da kowa zai yi wahala.
Lauyoyin Saipov sun roƙi lauya ya ƙi ɗaukan hukuncin kisa.
