Ya ce: "Yanzu yanayin ya ɗan daidaita kuma an samu kwanciyar hankali, saboda ci gaba da aka samu a yaƙi da ta'addanci.
Gwamnati tana ci gaba da gyara wuraren da ɓarayi suka lalata don a sake samun kwanciyar hankali.
Yanzu, 'yan gudun hijira suna iya komawa ƙasarsu, inda suka gudu daga ta'addanci da kuma matsalar tattalin arziki da ke sa biyan bukatun iyalansu ya zama musu da wuya.
Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya ta ce mutane miliyan 5.5 ne suka gudu daga ƙasar Siriya tun lokacin da aka soma yaƙin a shekara ta 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suke cikin ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta yi farin ciki da taimakon da za a ba su don a sake gina ƙasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya bayyana cewa ba za su karɓi taimako daga ƙasashen da suke goyon bayan tawaye ba.
Turai ta ci kofin Ryder Cup, a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe kofin Ryder Cup na 2018 inda ta doke Team USA da ci 16.5 yayin da USA ta doke 10.5, yayin da suke wasa a Le Golf National kusa da Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu, an ci Amurka a Turai sau shida a jere, kuma ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai a shekara ta 1993.
Turai ta yi nasara sa'ad da kyaftin din Denmark, Thomas Bjorn ya ci kwallo 14.5 da ake bukata don ya ci Amirka.
Phil Mickelson, ɗan wasan Amurka, ya kammala wasan da ƙwallo mai ƙarfi bayan ya jefa ƙwallo na farko a cikin ruwa a kan rami na 16, sai Francesco Molinari ya ci.
Molinari ɗan Italiya ya yi nasara sosai a wasan, shi ne ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasan huɗu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka soma wasan a shekara ta 1979.
Jordan Spieth ɗan Amirka ya yi nasara a 5 da 4 a kan ɗan wasa Thorbjorn Olesen ɗan Denmark da ke rukunin Turai.
Dustin Johnson, ɗan wasa mafi kyau a duniya, ya yi nasara da ƙwallon ƙafa biyu da ɗaya a kan ɗan Ingila Ian Poulter, wanda wataƙila shi ne ɗan wasan Ryder Cup na ƙarshe.
Sergio Garcia ɗan ƙasar Sifen wanda ya ci kofin Ryder sau takwas, shi ne ɗan wasa mafi nasara a Turai, kuma ya ci maki 25.5.
Ba na yawan yin kuka, amma a yau ba na iya kame kaina.
Kuma lokacin rani yana da wuya.
Na gode wa Thomas don ya ɗauke ni kuma ya nuna cewa ya amince da ni.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da na sake samun wannan kyautar.
"Suna da nasara, kuma ina alfahari da cewa na taimaka wajen samun nasara", in ji Garcia, wanda ya damu da nasarar Turai.
Ya mika kyautar ga abokin wasansa John Ram wanda ya doke Tiger Woods, gwarzon dan wasan golf na Amurka, 2&1 a ranar Lahadi a wasan mutum daya.
Rahm, ɗan shekara 23 ya ce: "Ina alfahari sosai da na ci Tiger Woods, na ga yadda yake wasa.
Woods ya yi nasara a wasanni hudu da ya yi a Faransa kuma a yanzu yana da tarihin 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wannan tarihin ya ba da tabbaci cewa wani ɗan wasa ne ya ci kofin duniya sau 14 kuma Jack Nicklaus ne ya ci lambar.
Ƙungiyar Amirka ta yi ta kokawa sosai a wannan makon sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas, da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasa mai kyau a wasan.
Kaftin din tawagar Amurka Jim Furyk ya ce bayan wasan da tawagarsa ta yi, 'Ina alfahari da 'yan'uwana da suka yi yaƙi.
A wannan safiya mun yi mamakin tawagar Turai.
Mun yi ƙoƙari.
Sai muka ba Thomas abin sha.
Shi kyaftin ne mai kyau.
Dukan 'yan wasan 12 da ya yi wasa da su sun yi kyau sosai.
Za mu sake zabar kanmu, zan yi aiki da PGA na Amurka da Kwamitin Ryder Cup ɗinmu kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina son 'yan'uwana 12 kuma ina farin cikin yin hidima tare da su.
Ya kamata mu daraja su.
Wasan ya ci mu.
Ƙarƙashin gurɓataccen ruwa a Pinellas, Manatee, da Sarasota
Wani rahoto na kwanan nan daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dabbobin Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa yawan gurɓataccen ruwa na teku ya ragu a yankunan da ke kusa da Tampa Bay.
FWC ta ce, an ba da rahoton cewa a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte, da kuma Collier, an ga alamun da ke nuna cewa gurɓataccen teku yana raguwa.
An kimanta cewa yankin da ke da gurɓataccen ruwa na teku yana da nisan mil 130 a bakin teku daga arewacin Pinellas zuwa kudu na Lee.
An gano wuraren da ake da alamun a kusan mil goma daga gabar teku a gundumar Hillsborough da kuma wasu wurare a makon da ya gabata.
An kuma lura da gurɓataccen ruwan teku a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata an ba da rahoton cewa an samu matsakaicin yanayin gurɓataccen ruwa a gefen gabar teku na Pinellas County, matsakaicin zuwa matsakaicin a gefen Hillsborough County, matsakaicin zuwa matsakaicin a cikin Manatee County, matsakaicin zuwa matsakaicin a gefen gabar teku na Sarasota County, matsakaicin zuwa matsakaicin a gefen gabar teku na Charlotte County, matsakaicin zuwa matsakaicin a gefen gabar teku na Lee County, da matsakaicin zuwa matsakaicin a cikin Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni game da matsalolin numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee, da kuma Collier.
Ba a taɓa samun rahoton ciwon numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata ba.
